## Quick Reference Cheat Sheet

```
VPC          → Isolated virtual network
Subnet       → Segment of VPC (public or private)
IGW          → Internet ↔ Public subnet
NAT Gateway  → Private subnet → Internet (outbound only)
NACL         → Stateless firewall at subnet level
Security Grp → Stateful firewall at instance level
VPC Endpoint → Private access to AWS services (S3, DynamoDB)
Bastion Host → Secure jump server for private subnet access
IAM Role     → Temporary credentials for AWS services/users
IAM Policy   → JSON permission document
```
